data.text:
High school in Boca: He was born in Omaha, Nebraska, and lived in Austin, Texas, from age 4 through 11. His family then moved to Boca Raton. He attended Boca Prep and graduated in 2000.

His pro debut: He played in the Delray Beach International Tennis Championships as a 17-year-old wild-card entry in 2000.
